LINK: https://www.namastesql.com/coding-problem/8-library-borrowing-habits?question_type=0&level_id=82791DA7C5D439BA

==> My approach:
select b1.BorrowerName
     , STRING_AGG(b2.BookName, ', ' ORDER BY b2.BookName) AS borrowedbooks              
FROM Borrowers AS b1
JOIN Books AS b2
ON b1.BookID = b2.BookID
GROUP BY b1.BorrowerName
ORDER BY BorrowerName; 
